  <h1>About the Dog Breeds App</h1>
  <p>Welcome to the Dog Breeds App, a platform dedicated to providing comprehensive information on various dog breeds worldwide. This application allows users to explore breed characteristics, learn about their origins, and see what other users think of each breed.</p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Search and Filter:</strong> Easily search for dog breeds by name, group, size, or purpose. Use alphabetical filters for quick navigation.</li>
    <li><strong>Breed Details:</strong> View detailed information about each breed, including sub-breeds when applicable.</li>
    <li><strong>User Comments:</strong> See what other users have to say about different breeds and share your own insights by leaving comments as a registered user.</li>
    <li><strong>Interactive Mapping:</strong> Explore user locations on an interactive map, providing a global perspective of user engagement.</li>
    <li><strong>Pagination:</strong> Browse through large collections of breeds and comments with smooth pagination.</li>
    <li><strong>Mobile Friendly:</strong> The app is fully responsive, providing a seamless experience across devices.</li>
  </ul>
